data.description:
Beautiful home with upgrades nestled in Plano's east side adjacent to greenbelt, jogging-biking paths, and approximately 3 blocks from Plano ISD's International Baccalaureate World School (PESH).  Wood flooring in entry, porcelain tile, remodeled kitchen with granite, backsplash, and sink.  Vinyl fencing, sprinkler system, wood replacement and complete exterior painting in the summer of 2023.  A new Lennox AC unit (Condenser, refrigerant, etc.) installed August 2023.  In addition to the other changes and upgrades, Olshan company improved the foundation (Installed 16 exterior Pilings) in January 2023 which includes a conditional Lifetime Service Foundation Warranty...Yes, the warranty is transferable.  
**The right buyer(s) could assume the sellers existing mortgage loan at 2.75% interest rate.  Contact the listing agent by email or text with any questions**   
Owner is a licensed real estate agent.
